Package: pipevizr
Type: Package
Title: Interactive Visualization of dplyr Pipelines
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Pete", "Benbow", email = "pebenbow@davidson.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create interactive visualizations of dplyr data transformation 
    pipelines. Shows each transformation step with expandable details, allowing
    users to understand complex data workflows at a glance.
